  "datePublished": "2026-04-27",
  "description": "The foundational operation of liberal thought that treats things as discrete substances with inherent properties — pre-relational, pre-political, sovereign over themselves — and so makes the world into a collection of independently-existing entities that can subsequently 'enter into' relations.",
